>\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qDMyMCg7M5k/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FqDMyMCg7M5k%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=f6e74f44&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"呢隻一開始唔識玩先難姐<br />\nGb 最難你要試下玩電梯大盜，我上網都搵唔到爆機video <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550389303d25740646810d62d0a5835038791c22","tid":1075814,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f2fd34678b0e08fa0c732d23d36a72edca532e","tid":1075814,"uid":137871,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:08:59.000Z","msg":"Hotline miami"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:32:15.000Z","msg":"1定2難"},{"pid":"6fc7d8f003d0675bba505c0b9d08316a1fa19246","tid":1075814,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c9bba0239b8d0631564135718cf8f5a38325602","tid":1075814,"uid":48500,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"9b71a191715d8e3ad9abba20ae65c828a6e0fd0c","tid":1075814,"uid":209890,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:26:04.000Z","msg":"香港人online<br />\n<br />\n首抽唔靚  重刷好大代價"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:20:44.000Z","msg":"香港係最難咁非洲國家係乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:40:36.000Z","msg":"輕鬆刷首抽"},{"pid":"064fca592a0e2e5868c0e9eefbe830b36e4974aa","tid":1075814,"uid":198200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"Cloudberry Kingdom"},{"pid":"4f4260fd7781896d0fcbd9caa931920494fa62c4","tid":1075814,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:52:48.000Z","msg":"竟然唔記得左getting over it 玩左10個鐘先爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c98552f69dbb97d0e005b2fbf4b051ed7604e2","tid":1075814,"uid":144024,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"竟然無ninja gaiden sigma <br />\n<br />\n我打機永遠都一開波有幾難揀幾難，玩呢隻一開波揀hard mode ，一開波嗰兩隻卒都差啲搞掂我，殘血去到第二個screen就瓜咗。之後慢慢掌握個技巧打落去，中間死咗起碼幾百次。<br />\n<br />\n好記得中間有幾個chapter 會用條大波妹。<br />\n咁條大波妹就拎廉刀嘅，郁得慢，但攻擊力高嗰種。<br />\n喺一隻對手啲怪係忍者、全撚部快過曱甴，你攻擊點高但係慢始終都無鳩用。算喇，慢慢磨都過到關嘅。<br />\n<br />\n但有關大佬真係打到而家都記得：<br />\n快撚到仆街就例牌，條撚樣仲會同你拉打，拉遠距離用枝手槍仔係咁啪（擋住就少少血咁扣）。咁你用嗰條大波妹當然係無長距離武器啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪唯有慢慢碌過去斬佢。但你一埋身，條撚樣就拎棍扑柒你，當然，你拎老鏈咁大把廉刀，起手當然無佢咁快。佢扑完你幾棍之後就會一腳踢翻你走，之後又用過槍啪過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我打呢隻boss打咗成個鳩幾鐘都打唔贏，最後死死地氣上網搵攻略（嗰陣邊有youtube，只得文字攻略）。我好撚記得嗰陣個攻略寫：<br />\n<br />\nThe attack pattern of the boss is very predictable but his  quick speed makes this fight a very difficult one. There are no known walkthrough at this moment and I wish you luck defeating this boss.<br />\n<br />\n連攻略都搞唔撚掂呀，仆街。<br />\n<br />\n最後load上一個save point 洗卒洗到成身藥水同佢命搏命先過到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： 我知呢隻可能未算最難，但對我黎講真係好深刻"},{"pid":"f1ea5499cfe2a71e22a50d9966dc9551f86e627b","tid":1075814,"uid":74970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:55:20.000Z","msg":"其實DMC5今集都好難<br />\n要精通咁多招, 風格, 武器互換, 打得靚又流暢好難"},{"pid":"73915e8d5a394177729761af383fabee1d835c1d","tid":1075814,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:58:05.000Z","msg":"I wanna be the boshy"},{"pid":"5cc0dc9d56a14b48541e668c39b1b91aec035aa1","tid":1075814,"uid":191150,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;做人&rdquo;最難玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb944c0c043855eb2c6b17cef1a2301833d3335","tid":1075814,"uid":244113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:05:49.000Z","msg":"celeste"},{"pid":"59c701c6cd5549b9400dfe274ec19a2eeba771