r />\n第一次打夢版lost kin 打咗三個鐘都贏唔到<br />\n直到拎左毒氣之後先打得贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次過path of pain<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/a5EUUB5_HwY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fa5EUUB5_HwY&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8jv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=537d0f11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/a5EUUB5_HwY</a>"},{"pid":"977a52e0060f790b517fe3ba99d5363ce2f2709a","tid":1075814,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:26:21.000Z","msg":"洛克人"},{"pid":"6a44856acdfbf936750a4c1777a7e7d83fb67c17","tid":1075814,"uid":75802,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0ny936.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0ny936.png&h=74670dbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48774644f713ae43ada339aec28e27cf8b1d97e2","tid":1075814,"uid":119996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:43:35.000Z","msg":"dota2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c955ed930aa0611ead282cc69d794faca1ba1f09","tid":1075814,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19c98552f69dbb97d0e005b2fbf4b051ed7604e2","tid":1075814,"uid":144024,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"竟然無ninja gaiden sigma <br />\n<br />\n我打機永遠都一開波有幾難揀幾難，玩呢隻一開波揀hard mode ，一開波嗰兩隻卒都差啲搞掂我，殘血去到第二個screen就瓜咗。之後慢慢掌握個技巧打落去，中間死咗起碼幾百次。<br />\n<br />\n好記得中間有幾個chapter 會用條大波妹。<br />\n咁條大波妹就拎廉刀嘅，郁得慢，但攻擊力高嗰種。<br />\n喺一隻對手啲怪係忍者、全撚部快過曱甴，你攻擊點高但係慢始終都無鳩用。算喇，慢慢磨都過到關嘅。<br />\n<br />\n但有關大佬真係打到而家都記得：<br />\n快撚到仆街就例牌，條撚樣仲會同你拉打，拉遠距離用枝手槍仔係咁啪（擋住就少少血咁扣）。咁你用嗰條大波妹當然係無長距離武器啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪唯有慢慢碌過去斬佢。但你一埋身，條撚樣就拎棍扑柒你，當然，你拎老鏈咁大把廉刀，起手當然無佢咁快。佢扑完你幾棍之後就會一腳踢翻你走，之後又用過槍啪過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我打呢隻boss打咗成個鳩幾鐘都打唔贏，最後死死地氣上網搵攻略（嗰陣邊有youtube，只得文字攻略）。我好撚記得嗰陣個攻略寫：<br />\n<br />\nThe attack pattern of the boss is very predictable but his  quick speed makes this fight a very difficult one. There are no known walkthrough at this moment and I wish you luck defeating this boss.<br />\n<br />\n連攻略都搞唔撚掂呀，仆街。<br />\n<br />\n最後load上一個save point 洗卒洗到成身藥水同佢命搏命先過到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： 我知呢隻可能未算最難，但對我黎講真係好深刻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:43:57.000Z","msg":"Ninja Gaiden Sigma真心正<br />\n玩難上一個難度爆機<br />\n轉玩難個陣比2隻兵SM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死多就冇玩到<br />\n<br />\n仲記得挑戰mode尾2定3難度就已經打唔贏<br />\n打後啲content冇打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2336cfc87dcb0ada481f26c88dc5d7e364ce4a23","tid":1075814,"uid":199304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:54:02.000Z","msg":"成日覺得玩呢啲game<br />\n係個game玩緊你多過你玩緊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42be95b9bf66406250b676cebcd3715bce9aabb7","tid":1075814,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:56:46.000Z","msg":"LF2"},{"pid":"87705834b1152a030ab7acb4036a05c9a78625a1","tid":1075814,"uid":38271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:00:11.000Z","msg":"怒首領蜂大往生"},{"pid":"97f9089ec06da0c061a490deaf6b76e6b7086b41","tid":1075814,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:09:18.000Z","msg":"CIRCUS CHARLIE<br />\nrainbow islands taito"},{"pid":"254ae9f43e4ab770dc585cbb143513b98684609a","tid":1075814,"uid":39608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:24:46.000Z","msg":"Mario cat"},{"pid":"f727013ef9